Cyanide looked to Halucigen immeidiately realizing hes responsible 
for the holograms that were otuside he then points his palm at the 
bot as eneergy gathered there.

Cyanide: "Oh no you don't."

And with that said a massive acid beam was fired directly at 
halucigen who was only a few steps away from him.

As that happened a loud clang was heard above everyone as a massive  
pink scoprion thing stared down at cygnar, ignatius, and Halucigen, 
the two metallic claws stretched a bit revelaing twin laser gattling 
guns between each and a wierd tank turret ontop. Inside of it Skywarp 
sits and smirks as he locks on to Cygnar.

Skywarp: "Leave... now..."
